    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Sometimes you just need to get a big boom down range. 6th Street is a primary supplier for these, and they just keep falling off of trucks headed for the Norcal Military Base, somehow.</p><p>A mortar emplacement can't be moved while set up, can't be moved while loaded, and requires an action to set up or break down. Once set up in this way, it's an exotic grenade launcher which uses the sniper rifle DV table, and can be fired with the Demolitions skill instead of the Heavy Weapons skill. Despite being an exotic weapon, it's still capable of firing non-basic ammunition.</p><p>The emplacement fires straight up, and straight down - it can't be used indoors, and can't target an area closer than 40m away.</p>"
